title: The Face Of Deception (Eve Duncan #1)
description:
An unidentified skull...

A trail of terrifying secrets...

And a woman whose talented hands could reveal the shocking truth...

As a forensic sculptor, Eve Duncan helps identify the dead from their
skulls. Her own daughter murdered and her body never found, the job
is Eve's way of coming to terms with her personal nightmare. But more
terror lies ahead when she accepts work from billionaire John Logan.
